{"tid":1567600,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【請全拋罷買呢場比賽】畜牲何君堯主人天祿周三夜馬(918)報名上陣","createTime":"2019-09-14T06:31:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T03:40:38.000Z","uid":37528,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"427d5e5abda8b3fef27e3873f5a7eff7c33794a9","tid":1567600,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:31:39.000Z","msg":"馬會今日（12日）公佈下周三（18日）谷草賽事報名馬，二班1000米賽事告東尼將派出「天祿」上陣。<br />\n<br />\n「天祿」由三人合股購入，包括何偉誠、李星強及何君堯。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯被指涉嫌是7.21元朗襲擊事件之幕後黑手，這宗事件導致最少45人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯周三會否親身進場為「天祿」打氣？將是全城焦點。<br />\n<br />\n至於馬會當晚會否加強保安，亦受到各界關注！<br />\n<br />\n求下大家唔好買呢一場比賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee3a2b647aa39dba175e7703ffcf87de19f2f388","tid":1567600,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:41:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"895f336e3dc5e23b4d235213d857a54f1c32f0bd","tid":1567600,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:47:10.000Z","msg":"支持斷腳"},{"pid":"b0178ada572478d30f1e4a3ee14c6e691897013b","tid":1567600,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:48:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span> <br />\n【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ccFUCqw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FccFUCqw.jpg&h=f44c3870&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7